    "For example, on the MS MARCO dataset, GENRE achieves a Recall@1 of 0.266 and an MRR@10 of 0.361, which are significantly lower than TSGen (Recall@1 = 0.384, MRR@10 = 0.502) and LTRGR (Recall@1 = 0.327, MRR@10 = 0.463).",
    "The lower performance of methods utilizing simpler DocID designs (e.g.",
